songs.title: Dreamers
songs.lyrics:
[Spoken]
When I grow up, I wanna be a screenwriter
I wanna be a journalist
I wanna be a lion
I wanna be a lion
I am a lionness
I want to be a superhero
I am a superhero
I wanna be a singer
I wanna be a singer
I wanna be a boss
I wanna be a doctor
I wanna be the boss
I am strong
I am invincible
I'm a leader
I'm the boss of my own world
I want to be heard
I want to be heard
I will be heard
I will make myself heard
I create my own rules
I will work hard
I am nobody's princess
I wanna grow up and be president
I wanna be president
